{"content": "I need to multiply 256 \u00d7 321 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 256\u2081\u2081 to base 10**\n- 2\u00d711\u00b2 + 5\u00d711\u00b9 + 6\u00d711\u2070\n- 2\u00d7121 + 5\u00d711 + 6\u00d71\n- 242 + 55 + 6\n- 303\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 321\u2081\u2081 to base 10**\n- 3\u00d711\u00b2 + 2\u00d711\u00b9 + 1\u00d711\u2070\n- 3\u00d7121 + 2\u00d711 + 1\u00d71\n- 363 + 22 + 1\n- 386\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 303 \u00d7 386 = 116,958\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 116,958\u2081\u2080 to base 11**\n- 116,958 \u00f7 11 = 10,632 R 6\n- 10,632 \u00f7 11 = 966 R 6\n- 966 \u00f7 11 = 87 R 9\n- 87 \u00f7 11 = 7 R 10 (a)\n- 7 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 7\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 7a966\n\n**Answer: 7a966**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 358}